---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="服务 | Synapse 咨询与实施">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#FCAD2A] uppercase mb-4">SERVICES</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-4">让你的 AI 团队真正可靠地运转</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)] text-lg mb-12">基于 Harness Engineering 方法论，我们帮你从零搭建或优化现有的 AI Agent 管理体系。</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4 flex-wrap gap-4">
          <div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FCAD2A] bg-[#FCAD2A]/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">ASSESSMENT</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-3">Synapse Assessment</h2>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] text-sm mt-1">2天诊断评估</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FCAD2A]">$5K-$10K</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)] text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">评估您当前的 AI 使用现状和管理能力，对标 Harness Engineering 行业标准，输出定制化落地路径。</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] rounded-lg p-3"><span class="text-[#013A7D] font-semibold">AI 成熟度诊断</span><br><span class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">评估 AI 管理现状</span></div>
          <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] rounded-lg p-3"><span class="text-[#013A7D] font-semibold">差距分析</span><br><span class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">对标行业最佳实践</span></div>
          <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] rounded-lg p-3"><span class="text-[#013A7D] font-semibold">路线图建议</span><br><span class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">定制落地路径</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4 flex-wrap gap-4">
          <div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#028CDC] bg-[#028CDC]/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">IMPLEMENTATION</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-3">Synapse Implementation</h2>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] text-sm mt-1">2-4周体系落地</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#028CDC]">$30K-$80K</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)] text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">完整的 Synapse 体系落地实施，包含执行链、决策体系、Agent 团队、情报系统、HR 审计全套交付。</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] rounded-lg p-3"><span class="text-[#013A7D] font-semibold">Harness Configuration</span><br><span class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">定制执行链+决策体系</span></div>
          <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] rounded-lg p-3"><span class="text-[#013A7D] font-semibold">Agent 团队搭建</span><br><span class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">角色设计+能力标准</span></div>
          <div class="bg-[#F7F8FA] rounded-lg p-3"><span class="text-[#013A7D] font-semibold">情报+HR系统</span><br><span class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">自动化闭环+质量审计</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#013A7D] bg-[#013A7D]/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">INDUSTRY</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mt-3">建筑行业 AI 增值服务</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] text-sm mt-1 mb-4">Synapse 行业解决方案</p>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)] text-sm leading-relaxed">在建筑数字化交付项目中嵌入 AI 驱动的 PMO 管理 — 自动化 WBS 调度、AI 风险预警、智能交付物生成、阶段门质量管控。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="mailto:lysanderl@janusd.io?subject=Synapse%20咨询预约" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-[#FCAD2A] text-[#0A1628] rounded-lg font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">预约咨询</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
